		    =-=-=- Nethermancer -=-=-=

	Also known as a Death-Mage, the Nethermancer is a
hybrid spell caster. A Nethermancer gains his power from
the realm of the dead, through summoning, communing with,
and control of the dead. His spells focus on death, cold,
and undeath. Drain life, and wind of death are typical
Nethermancer spells.

Type:   Death/Undeath Spell Caster
Skills: Limited combat
Spells: Undead Summoning, Drain, unholy Attacks
Prime Attributes: Int, Wis

Comments: The Nethermancer have even more summoning spells 
    then Necromancers in the MUD. There whole existence 
    revolves around their powerful pets, which are the focus 
    of the majority of their spells.
